Adding automated accessibility testing to your site's build process is a key tool to maintaining and improving your site's accessibility. 

## Adding Lighthouse comparison tests to CI builds

How to add Lighthouse comparison tests to CI builds.

## External testing and reporting tools

External automated testing and reporting tools provide another way to confirm ongoing iterative work remains accessible and meets your organization's accessibility standards. 